‐ It's very lonely, Aine.

22:17.480 --> 22:19.920
You know, most of my friends,
half of them are dead.

22:23.280 --> 22:26.240
‐ Did you kill them?

22:26.240 --> 22:27.880
‐ Only Louise Gallagher,

22:27.880 --> 22:30.560
because she was
so fucking annoying.

22:30.560 --> 22:31.560
‐ [laughs]

22:31.560 --> 22:32.560
[phone buzzes]

22:32.560 --> 22:35.160
[gasps]

22:35.160 --> 22:36.200
Oh, my God, Mammy,
he texted back.

22:36.200 --> 22:38.360
‐ Go on.
What did he say?

22:38.360 --> 22:39.560
[mumbles]

22:41.120 --> 22:43.360
"Ha ha."

