God, that's a bit
of an anticlimax.

22:45.480 --> 22:46.680
Jesus.

22:46.680 --> 22:48.600
You have to be careful
with men.

22:48.600 --> 22:50.360
They don't always get jokes.

22:50.360 --> 22:52.080
‐ No.

