Also annoyingly, Shona didn't
get us return tickets.

22:54.560 --> 22:55.600
‐ What?
‐ Yeah.

22:55.600 --> 22:56.960
Don't worry, I'll get them.

22:56.960 --> 22:58.120
EILEEN:
No, I'm getting the tickets.

22:58.120 --> 22:59.560
AINE: No, Mammy,
I'm getting them.

22:59.560 --> 23:01.000
You're disabled,
so they will be half price.

23:01.000 --> 23:02.600
EILEEN: I am not disabled.
AINE: You are.

23:02.600 --> 23:04.000
EILEEN: I am getting
both tickets,

23:04.000 --> 23:05.800
and they will both be
full fare.

